# RoomCloud Sites Configuration
#
# List all WordPress sites that use RoomCloud integration.
# One site per line.
#
# Format:
#   Local sites:  /absolute/path/to/wordpress
#   Remote sites: user@hostname:/path/to/wordpress
#
# Lines starting with # are ignored (comments)
# Empty lines are ignored

# Example local sites:
/var/www/client1.com/public_html
/var/www/client2.com/public_html
/home/sites/client3

# Example remote sites (via SSH):
root@client4.com:/var/www/html
user@192.168.1.100:/var/www/client5
staging@staging-server:/home/staging/client6

# Add your 10 client sites below:
